column22: Saprobic, found especially on wood in both wet and dry habitats. column22: Saprobic, found especially on wood in both wet and dry habitats. column22: Saprobic, found especially on wood in both wet and dry habitats. column22: Saprobic, found especially on wood in both wet and dry habitats.
